Description: Deerfield Run & Village Square North in Laurel, MD are located at Route 197 and Contee Road. We offer big and bright 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments and 2 and 3 bedroom townhomes. We’re at the center of everything you need. Public transit is at your doorstep - Metro Bus 87 Express stops here with service to Greenbelt Metro station, RTA Bus 301 stops here with service to Town Centre at Laurel. 5 minutes to MARC Laurel commuter rail station (Camden line). 3 minutes to Baltimore-Washington Parkway, 5 minutes to I-495/ I-95 & MD 200 (ICC). Close to endless shopping, restaurants & services for everyday living. 10 minutes to Target, Wal-Mart, Sam's Club, Kohl's & Total Wine. Next door to Deerfield Run Community Center. 5 minutes to Montpelier Cultural Arts Center and Climb Zone indoor rock climbing facility. 10 minutes to Fairland Park with sports, aquatics and ice skating. Apartment features include a very spacious living area with room for lots of furniture, separate dining area with ceiling fan, many have nice views of landscaped courtyards or woods, fully-equipped kitchen with breakfast bar, walk-in or long wall closets, blinds provided throughout, and central heat and air conditioning. Gas and electricity are included in your rent – you pay water/sewer. Cats are welcome. Property features include a relaxing swimming pool with sundeck, colonial style architecture, laundry and mail delivery in each building, on-site management and 24-hour emergency maintenance. Two communities side-by-side managed by the same management company. For more information and availability, visit www.deerfieldrun-villagesquarenorth.com.

Description:
Move-in Special Discount for Unit #C: Rent at $1250/month for the first 3 months!
Rent without discount: $1400/month.
- WALKING DISTANCE FROM THE MARC TRAIN!
- GREAT LOCATION FOR UNIVERSITY STUDENTS!
- GREAT LOCATION FOR PERSONS WORKING AT FORT MEADE, JOHNS HOPKINS APPLIED PHYSICS LABORATORY, AND NASA!
Spacious apartment in the heart of Historic Laurel! Rent this renovated property today! Available IMMEDIATELY WITH NOTICE!
Rent is $1400 per month. This apartment is on a quiet area of Main Street, in the front (2nd floor) of a building with several private apartments. This unit is called the "Streetview Apartment" because it has a spectacular overlook of Main Street through large bay windows.
The apartment is approximately 950 square feet. The kitchen and living room are open with a wall-to-wall windows facing Main Street. One private bedroom. One Bathroom (shower with full tub).
Utilities: Tenant pays for electricity only. Water is included.
Apartment has washer and dryer, forced-air heat, AC, refrigerator, and stove / oven.
Renovations include: Updated painting (throughout the apartment), flooring (hallway only -- the large living area has the luscious original), and high-quality carpet in bedroom!
Sorry, no pets (except for medically-documented and required animals, such as seeing eye and emotional support animals) and no smoking.
Verizon Fios available in this area!
Discounts available for active duty military personnel, teachers, and public safety personnel. Please inquire for additional details.
Security deposit MAY be waived with documentation of excellent credit history and/or consistent employment. Offer is for a limited time. Please inquire for additional details (income must be at least three times the monthly rent, no criminal background, and no prior evictions, and further criteria).
Right across the street and on the same block: an excellent Mediterranean restaurant and bar, convenience store, hair salon, Laurel Playhouse (community theatre).
Apartment is available IMMEDIATELY WITH NOTICE!
Please contact Pamela by text message (preferred), phone call, or email.
If responding by email, please refer to the "Streetview Apartment."
NEIGHBORHOOD and other Geographical Information:
Very accessible neighborhood:
Close to several main roads of interest: US-1/Baltimore Ave, MD-198/Fort Meade Rd, MD-197/Laurel-Bowie Rd (via MD-198), MD-32 Patuxent Freeway, MD-200/Inter-County Connector.
Nearby Highways: I-95 (to I-495 and I-695 Beltways), I-295/Baltimore-Washington Parkway.
Nearby to BWI Thurgood Marshall International Airport (~ 20 min).
Commuter Access: MARC train, Buses 302 (to FDA / Muirkirk), and 89/89M (Greenbelt Metro Station).
Main Street (within walking distance): A GREAT walking and bike path, 2 blocks away and runs alongside the Patuxent River! Also, numerous local eateries and markets, a post office, community theater (right across the street!), hair salons, professional offices, and miscellaneous businesses. Join the Main Street community!
Within Driving Distance: The new Towne Centre at Laurel (Regal Cinemas, Harris Teeter, Sports Authority, Mission BBQ, Noodles & Co., Nando's, Outback Steakhouse, Blaze Pizza, Massage Envy); Laurel Shopping Center (Giant Food, LA Fitness, Starbucks, banks and restaurants), Library, other restaurants (Sardi's and Chipotle), pharmacies, the Dutch Country Farmer's Market, Planet Fitness, and many other businesses and professional services.
Ideal for persons working at Fort Meade, Johns Hopkins Applied Physics Laboratory, and the NSA.
Welcome to the City of Laurel, where 4 counties - Prince George's, Montgomery, Howard, and Anne Arundel - are in easy reach, and midway between Washington, DC and Baltimore.
Apartment is available IMMEDIATELY WITH NOTICE!
Please contact Pamela by text message (preferred), phone call, or email.
If responding by email, please refer to the "Streetview Apartment."
We look forward to showing this apartment to you; it won't be on the market for long!

Description:
Renting 2 spacious rooms out to individual students or working professionals. House is in great condition, clean and spacious 2000 sqft home on Patuxent Green Golf Course in Laurel. Back deck and yard are beautiful for grilling and relaxing in a nice quiet neighborhood. Walking paths are next to the house along the golf course and scenic areas of the neighborhood or go for a walk on the golf course.
Tenants split utilities electric/water/verizon. Must pass a background check. Ideal for single student or working professional. Room occupancy is 1 tenant per room - No live-in guests of tenants, no pets. The house is partially furnished but tenants will need their own individual room furniture.

Description: Located in the center of Maryland and the Nation’s Capital, Ashbury Courts brings convenience and luxury to North Laurel, Maryland in Howard County. Located right on Route 1, Ashbury Courts Apartments, a pet friendly community, offers incredibly convenient access for commuters to greater DC and Baltimore with the best value of any apartment building in the area. We are close to Fort Meade, I-95 and the Beltway. Fitness Room, Media Room and Billiards Room with NO AMENITY FEES. All kitchens have granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and wood floors. If you are looking for the best deal in the area, look no further. We have the nicest living space for the most reasonable prices. Ashbury Courts offers Condo living at affordable apartment pricing.Six Reasons Why You Should Choose Us: 1.	Health Club-style Fitness Center 2.	Granite & Stainless Steel in Kitchens 3.	Outdoor seating and BBQ Areas 4.	Full-sized Washers & Dryers 5.	Controlled Access Entry 6.	First Floor Retail

Description: Now Leasing! Brand new, luxury apartment homes in the heart of Laurel, Maryland. All of our beautifully designed luxury apartment homes include upgraded, modern interior finishes including granite countertops, custom tile backsplashes, maple cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, a washer and dryer, oversized windows and contemporary lighting features. C Street Flats is located in Laurel, Maryland's Historical District. We are centrally located between Washington, DC and Baltimore; with a two minute walk from your front door to the MARC Train, which services both cities. Our convenient location allows you to enjoy the best that Laurel has to offer, all within walking or biking distance. Call us today to find out why you will LOVE coming home to C Street Flats!

Ideal commuting to Ft. Meade, University of Maryland College Park, and Greenbelt Metro. Close to restaurants, shopping, and the Towne Centre at Laurel Accepts Section 8.

Community recreation areas that include: parks and playgrounds. Easy access to Interstate 95, Main Street MARC Train station, restaurants, libraries; close to Ft. Meade and the new Laurel Town Center. Available for rent NOW so do not wait! Schedule your tour today!

Description:
---- SCHEDULE A SHOWING ONLINE AT: http://showmojo.com/lac/50391b703b ----
You've probably seen many properties as you hunt for a new close-to-everything home. Look no further, this first time rental has everything...well located, lots of room, and the right price!
First, let's look at its size: huge end unit with 4 large bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bathrooms. Over 3200 square feet! 
Next, neighborhood: highly sought after Emerson. Brief commute to Columbia and Fort Meade. Convenient to Rt. 29, Rt. 1, 295 and 95
Lastly, its other highlights: Hardwood floors on main level, gorgeous gourmet kitchen with exquisite tile work, breakfast nook, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops. Kitchen opens to large living/dining area with gas fireplace. Huge master suite with large master bath, soaking tub and separate shower. Spacious finished lower level with full bath and bedroom. Large bedrooms (each fits a full size bed!) Two car garage. 
With so many great features, this townhouse will go very quickly. Don't miss this opportunity. Schedule a showing today!
NOTE: Two year lease preferred!

Description:
Ready to rent! This spacious end-unit townhouse is conveniently located in the desirable, secure Russett Green neighborhood near great schools and close proximity to Ft. Meade, NSA, Baltimore and DC. The home features a gorgeous updated open floor plan, with separate dining and living areas. Host your guests on the lovely open deck overlooking the backyard and community playground. The first floor has an updated Â½ bath with new fixtures, a spacious living room/rec room and a separate laundry suite. The second floor also features a beautiful eat in kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space and all stainless steel appliances. The third floor has three spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space, and an updated full bath with custom tiled floor. The master bedroom has it's own master bathroom suite with soaking tub and walk-in shower, as well as "his-and-hers" sinks.
Utilities: Tenant pays for electric and water.
Call or email today to schedule a showing!

leasing@realpropertymetro.com

Description:
Great home on a tree lined cul-de-sac. Backs to trees with a fenced in yard and spacious deck for entertaining. Walking distance to the library. Huge finished basement with a lower level fireplace is great for hosting when the weather isn't cooperating. 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths this home is a great place to live. Minutes to Rts. 32 and 95. 
Living space galore! 3 finished levels with rear deck and private fenced in backyard. Basement is complete with a fireplace in the rec room as well as full size laundry and room for a home office. Generous kitchen features a built in island and yards of countertop space. Powder room off the living room is tucked away. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths top out the upstairs.

Description: We at Westgate of Laurel Apartments take pride in taking care of the details, so you can relax and simply take care of living. It's more than a roof over your head. It's part of your life and we never forget that. Westgate of Laurel offers efficiencies, 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments for rent in Laurel, Maryland. Washer and Dryer in Every Apartment...Newly Remodeled Kitchens...Daycare on Site. Convenience and amenities spell "luxury living". Close to schools, shopping, and public transportation. Located 1/2 mile from I-95 to Baltimore or Washington and near Baltimore/Washington Parkway, Ft. Meade, Andrews AFB, Walter Reed and NSA! Locations that make sense for the way you live. Historic Main Street fills your days with antiquing and artesian shops, while nights are reserved for fine-dining experiences and the entertainment offered by the greater Laurel area.

Description:
Enjoy the quiet comfort that our one bedroom senior 55+ apartments have to offer. Brimming with abundant space and ample features, these homes were designed to best accommodate your needs. The Laurel Lakes senior apartment community is an ideal place for today’s seniors. Whether you want to partake in one of our planned activities or service programs, or independently use our computer lab or garden areas, there’s something for everyone. Apartment features include Attractive, fully-equipped kitchens, decorative mini blinds/some with verticals
Highly-efficient, individually controlled heating and cooling systems, safety features including emergency pull cords, grab bars, smoke detectors and sprinkler system.
Cable hook-ups in bedroom and living room
Wall-to-wall carpeting
Ceramic tiled bathrooms equipped with grab bars
Some handicapped-accessible

Description: Laurel Gardens is tucked away in a wonderful residential area, the brand new construction community is designed with you in mind. Our BRAND NEW apartments are unique with stylish and convenient features, Washer & Dryers in every apartment home, Vaulted Ceilings on top floors, an excellent staff all tucked away in a gorgeous location. A commuter's dream quick commute to either Baltimore or Washington DC. Easy commute to Fort Meade, NSA and Johns Hopkins Applied Physics Lab as well as being just minutes away to many public amenities! Come home to Laurel Gardens today!
